      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus drawn from coupon test data (N=20 coupons). Geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of production screws. Monte Carlo UQ (10,000 samples) propagates all input distributions to construct-level QoIs, yielding 95% prediction intervals reported alongside point estimates. Input distributions assumed independent normal; no sensitivity analysis was conducted to rank input contributions to output variance."
